The paper deals with image classification using Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs), which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses text recognition and Optical Character Recognition (OCR), which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of CNNs for classification is a machine learning technique, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and deep learning (cs.DL).
